Just A Morpher - A morpher for x86 WoW.

After building, use any DLL injector to inject it into WoW.

It adds the following API functions to WoW:

-- Set a unit's display ID.
SetDisplayID (UnitID, DisplayID)

-- Get a unit's display ID.
GetDisplayID (UnitID)

-- Get a unit's native display ID.
GetNativeDisplayID (UnitID)

-- Set a unit's scale.
SetScale (UnitID, Scale)

-- Get a unit's scale.
GetScale (UnitID)

-- Set a unit's mount's display ID.
SetMountDisplayID (UnitID, DisplayID)

-- Get a unit's mount's display ID.
GetMountDisplayID (UnitID)

-- Set the display ID of a unit's item.
SetItemDisplayID (UnitID, Item, DisplayID)

-- Get the display ID of a unit's item.
GetItemDisplayID (UnitID, Item)

-- Update a unit's model.
UpdateModel (UnitID)

Items:

Head = 0
Shoulders = 2
Shirt = 3
Chest = 4
Waist = 5
Legs = 6
Feet = 7
Wrists = 8
Hands = 9
Back = 14
MainHand = 15
OffHand = 16
Ranged = 17
Tabard = 18